an'; font-size:11pt">. </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">This was followed </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">a year later </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">by the</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">‘Climategate affair’ </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">that </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">exposed </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">the same </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">institutions and so-called ‘climate scientists’</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">transgressing</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">their responsibilities to </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">science ethics. T</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">he climategate </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">revelation</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">s</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">were</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt"> a </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">seminal moment</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt"> that</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">reinforced </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">deep scepticism</span><span style="font-family:'Tim