w Roman'; font-size:11pt">e could be expanded upon but </span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">is limited in word number by </span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">STSC Committee </span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">diktat.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; font-style:italic">April 2013</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold">Bibliography</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; font-weight:bold">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">Andrew M Montford PhD – ‘The Hockey Stick Illusion’ –</span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt"> 2010, </span><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">ISBN 978 1 906768 35 5</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="background-color:#ffffff; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="backgrou